    "description": "Break a leg is a game where your goal is to break a leg. In this game, you can also jump on trampolines, press keys to do funny things like do drugs and divorce your wife. There's also a baby hidden in the map that you can feed uranium and plutonium to! You really beat the game though when you break your leg.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen you break your leg, no need to keep playing - you win when you break your leg! It's easy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game is 1 of many games that are going to be &quot;Literal&quot; games. This was also uploaded to YouTube as a YouTube shorts series where the top comment got the next addition to the game. Which is why there's so many weird things.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBreak a leg is a game where when you break your leg, you hear a scream and the character broke his leg! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nBreak a leg is a meme game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBreak a leg is not meant to be taken seriously!",
